text: Přístav is a Czech television programme which was first broadcast in 2015. In the Czech language přístav means port. The programme was written by various writers and directed by Jana Rezková (2015–2017), Jaromír Polisenský (2015–2016) and Ján Novák (2015–2016). The series was nominated as Best Television Drama at the 2015 Czech Lion Awards.
